@page "/nodes"

<PageTitle>Nodes</PageTitle>

<div class="space-y-6">
    <header class="space-y-3">
        <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-signal-600">Cutover</p>
            <h1 class="font-display text-4xl text-cinder-950 sm:text-5xl">Legacy nodes page retired</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="max-w-5xl text-base leading-8 text-cinder-800">
            Node discovery, filtering, favorites, and detail drill-down no longer belong to the server-rendered UI.
            Those flows are being moved to the browser-first client and local projection stores.
        </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid gap-4 xl:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]">
        <article class="liquid-panel rounded-[1.6rem] p-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-cinder-950">Removed from the server path</h2>
            <ul class="mt-5 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-cinder-800/84">
                <li>Node table filtering, pagination, and telemetry rendering.</li>
                <li>Inline favorite toggles and server-side detail modals.</li>
                <li>Projection-driven refresh through Blazor notifier subscriptions.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="liquid-panel rounded-[1.6rem] p-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-cinder-950">Temporary server route</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-cinder-800/82">
                This route remains only as a migration marker while the remaining legacy pages are retired.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a href="/messages" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Messages</a>
                <a href="/map" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Map</a>
                <a href="/topics" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Topics</a>
            </div>
        </article>
    </section>
</div>
